---
description: Keep business-domain logic in app repos and infrastructure in AppModules
alwaysApply: true
---

# Modules vs App Ownership Boundary

- App repositories own business semantics, DTO meanings, and feature workflows.
- `AppModules` owns domain-agnostic infrastructure primitives only.
- Never place app-specific domain rules or value universes in `AppModules`.
- Extract code to `AppModules` only when it is infrastructure-level and cross-app reusable.
